== About me
Hello. I am a post-doc at [https://www.fudan.edu.cn/ Fudan University], working with [http://homepage.fudan.edu.cn/wggao/zh/ Prof. Weiguo Gao] and [http://www.sdspeople.fudan.edu.cn/weike/ Prof. Ke Wei]. 
Before that, I completed my Ph.D. in School of Physics at [http://www.bit.edu.cn/ Beijing Institute of Technology], 
where I worked with [http://physics.bit.edu.cn/szdw/zzjzg/fg/lyl/index.htm Prof. Yulong Liu]. 
I received B.E. in School of Information and Communication Engineering from [http://www.njit.edu.cn/ Nanjing Institute of Technology ].

== Research Interests
My research interests include 
- Compressed Sensing  
- High Dimensional Statistics and Probability
- Data Science

