. Jinchi Chen and Yulong Liu, [https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/abstract/document/8354890/ Data-Time Tradeoffs for Corrupted Sensing], IEEE Signal Processing Letters, 2018.
. Jinchi Chen and Yulong Liu, [https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/8006581 Corrupted sensing with sub-Gaussian measurements], 2017 IEEE International Symposium on Information Theory (ISIT), 2017.
